  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0db0\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0db8 \u0d9a\u0db3\u0dd4\u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dda",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "In the central hills",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Ranjith Alahakon, Assistant Director of Nuwara Eliya District Disaster Management Unit, said that due to the strong winds blowing through the western ridge area of \u200b\u200bthe central mountains and intermittent heavy rains, trees fell on several main roads and traffic was disrupted.",
        "A large cypress tree fell on the main road at the Nanuoyaya intersection of the Nuwara Eliya-Badulla main road.",
        "The army, police and local residents cut down a part of the cypress tree that had fallen on the main road and reduced the traffic to one lane.",
        "Meanwhile, a large eucalyptus tree fell on the main road in Maskeliya Kuda Maskeliya area of \u200b\u200bHatton Maskeliya main road and the traffic on that road was also disrupted."
      ],
